New-Item .gitignore -ItemType File
notepad .gitignore
```

Notepad will open. Paste this inside:
```
# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Keys and certificates
*.key
*.p12
ca.key
ca.crt
*.crt
*.sig

# Environment
.env
venv/
env/

# Uploads
uploads/

# VS Code
.vscode/

# Windows
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini